707470f-a.text:
Ave X, north side, between Stillwell Ave., and West 11th Street, showing a new development in this area of Coney Island. To the right, is Hubbard Creek, and in the background (high chimney) is the City incinerator for the area.
August 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
